title: Country - Original Soundtrack
description:
Ripped from the CD at 256kbs, mp3 with Front cover art.  I think it better than the review makes it sound.

 	
Charles Gross composed and conducted this score, but it's played by several of the new-age artists from Windham Hill Records, notably piantist George Winston, whose distinctive piano playing actually dominates the proceedings.
- Authored By William Ruhlmann
